                            <comment id="15213701" author="matthewlmcclure" created="Mon, 28 Mar 2016 01:09:21 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;I see one symptom of nonconformance to POSIX during &lt;tt&gt;vagrant provision&lt;/tt&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;

